==== SOURCE

https://help.netflix.com/en/node/100639

==== AGENT

Netflix movie recommendation

==== GOAL

Recommend movies a user might be interested in.

==== DATA

They collect data from each user such as when a user pause a video, what time of the day they watch, browsing and scrolling behaviour.

==== METHODS

They train their algorithm after every visit to Netflix to better predict the movie its user might watch.

==== RESULTS

They recommend movies they think the users will like more. They have high customer retention rate as a result.

==== COMMENTS

Netflix has good movie recommendations.